### §18.2 Candidate B step

蓝图：
```python
phi = compute_motion_potential(z, landscape, ledger)
m_eff = compute_effective_inertia(7 inputs)
delta_w = gate * (eta*external - decay*w - contradiction) / m_eff
audit_m_eff(phi, m_eff, delta_w)
```

当前实现：
- ✅ `m_eff = compute` (7 inputs via D1)
